data.description: This high quality home, located in north Knoxville, is full of potential and is in need of a few repairs. With six spacious bedrooms that include plentiful closet space, this property is sure to have enough room for family and friends! The open concept floor plan makes it the perfect home to entertain guests and makes the home feel so much bigger than it already is. An expansive privacy fenced back yard has room for play equipment, a garden, or even a private pool! Call or text listing agent with any additional questions. *This home has possible damage to the upstairs subfloor and lingering pet odors. Call or text the listing agent for additional information.Sq ft from tax records, buyer to verify ft and all other information.
